      "id": "mem-MEMORY-common-issues-found",
      "content": "- **Cron model routing bug**: Bare model names get prefixed with agent's primary provider. Always use fully-qualified: `google-gemini-cli/gemini-2.5-flash`, NOT `gemini-2.5-flash`\n- **Auth profile errors**: Check `usageStats.errorCount` and `cooldownUntil` fields - reset to 0/remove when updating tokens\n- **Atlas permissions**: Was too restricted. Now has full exec, fs, web, messaging, sessions access\n- **Kimi/Moonshot**: Keys consistently return 401. User needs to verify at Moonshot console.\n- ",
